description: Rabbit Crew Kenya is a pioneering rabbit farming initiative established in January 2019, focused on producing rabbit meat for the Kenyan market. The enterprise not only sells meat but also supports local farmers by providing training, breeding stock, and construction of rabbit hatches. With a commitment to enhancing food security and promoting sustainable farming practices, Rabbit Crew aims to educate communities about the nutritional benefits of rabbit meat while fostering a network of rabbit farmers across the region.
name: Rabbit Crew Kenya
